<p><img src="/assets/images/2016/ivnc-emails.jpg" alt="Photo of scheduling emails" /></p>

<p>Which were not always so polite, thanks to the pressures of planning, lack of sleep, and, in some cases, mad last second scrambling
to get better data plots ‚Äì but I‚Äôm pretty sure there‚Äôs some unwritten grad student rule somewhere that what happens during
conference week stays in conference week.</p>

<p>But the job also has its perks, like these extra bottles of wine that mysteriously made their way to our table during the banquet,
after it was made known to the catering staff which table was the volunteers‚Äô table.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/2016/ivnc-extra-wine.jpg" alt="Pictured: wine gift from the catering gods" />
